  <note reference-line="4" id="2">
    <original>diṭṭhappatto (ka.)</original>
    <type>auto</type>
    <snippet>‘‘Tayome, āvuso samiddha, puggalā santo saṃvijjamānā lokasmiṃ. Katame tayo? Kāyasakkhī, diṭṭhippatto </snippet>
