    </alternatives>
  </note>
  <note reference-line="11" id="4">
    <original>svāyaṃ (syā. kaṃ. pī.), soyaṃ (ka.)</original>
    <type>auto</type>
    <snippet> khvettha, sāriputta, sukaraṃ ekaṃsena byākātuṃ – ‘ayaṃ imesaṃ tiṇṇaṃ puggalānaṃ abhikkantataro ca paṇītataro cā’ti. Ṭhānañhetaṃ, sāriputta, vijjati yvāyaṃ puggalo saddhāvimutto svāssa </snippet>
    <match>svāssa</match>
    <alternatives>
